@prefix wd:   <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/> .

#############################################
# Wikidata sameAs links — verified batch 1 of N
# Added ALONGSIDE existing DBpedia owl:sameAs links (data/seed/people.ttl),
# not replacing them. Each entry below was individually verified against
# a live Wikidata search, not inferred from memory — Wikidata Q-numbers
# have no mnemonic structure, so guessing is genuinely risky (see
# Marcus Aurelius below: the plausible-looking "Marcus Aurelius Antoninus"
# search hit is a DISAMBIGUATION PAGE, Q1632736 — the real entity is Q1430).
#
# Remaining ~19 people/schools in people.ttl and expansion_2026-07-10.ttl
# still need this same check before adding — do NOT copy Q-numbers from
# memory for those. Verify each one the same way: search "<name> wikidata",
# confirm the description on the hit actually matches the person (not a
# namesake, disambiguation page, or different person by the same name),
# then add here.
#############################################

tgs:Person.EOWilson owl:sameAs wd:Q211029 .
tgs:Person.MarcusAurelius owl:sameAs wd:Q1430 .
